2.000539	Trình báo mất hộ chiếu phổ thông (thực hiện tại cấp trung ương)	Cấp Bộ\nTrình báo mất hộ chiếu phổ thông\nQuản lý xuất nhập cảnh\nTTHC không được luật giao cho địa phương quy định hoặc quy định chi tiết\nCông dân Việt Nam\nCục quản lý xuất nhập cảnh\nTrong thời hạn 02 ngày làm việc kể từ ngày phát hiện hộ chiếu phổ thông bị mất, người bị mất hộ chiếu trực tiếp nộp hoặc gửi đơn báo mất hộ chiếu theo mẫu cho Cục Quản lý xuất nhập cảnh hoặc trên môi trường điện tử tại Cổng dịch vụ công quốc gia hoặc Cổng dịch vụ công quốc gia hoặc Cổng dịch vụ công Bộ Công an. Trường hợp vì lý do bất khả kháng, thời hạn nộp hoặc gửi đơn báo mất có thể dài hơn nhưng trong đơn phải giải thích cụ thể về lý do bất khả kháng.\nKhông có thông tin	[0.045700993,0.062437087,-0.0362876,-0.06360887,0.10026982,0.029609304,-0.022603575,0.0372934,-0.010715616,0.04866308,0.052383184,-0.03896021,0.0075816377,-0.026789254,-0.005925236,-0.023396859,-0.018142521,0.050643638,0.045489185,-0.06364365,0.01940823,0.025095087,-0.059213266,0.033611692,0.058207504,0.039931353,-0.021152249,-0.028745607,-0.0023706895,-0.0017764211,-0.023560487,0.0189841,-0.072029226,0.011353689,0.08413861,-0.017119493,0.037675284,-0.01083717,0.027228164,-0.043283444,-0.0086209215,-0.0778621,-0.010802537,-0.031639863,0.028724188,0.044379435,-0.02228789,-0.044111274,-0.09637828,0.0048291013,0.105308756,-0.0064684507,0.037369233,0.087511614,-0.044066865,-0.013644642,0.014275152,0.04224894,-0.09424048,0.01794906,-0.082067385,-0.009068394,-0.065354064,-0.034767214,-0.075220026,0.06689587,-0.061831906,-0.050669618,0.021272428,-0.001652939,-0.075151,-0.03707297,-0.06597009,0.065631926,0.0025917666,-0.023982331,-0.012100281,0.14542559,0.07689576,-0.030664127,0.05801119,0.07653706,-0.030673085,-0.006486497,-0.05926175,-0.059174802,-0.08343673,0.074955866,-0.01612949,-0.03086528,0.080700755,0.0076203207,0.052265167,-9.5880685e-05,-0.02061345,-0.049672123,-0.0050433446,0.072334185,-0.041048415,0.122123376,0.089566916,0.056589827,-0.