2.001159	Thông báo lưu trú	Cấp Xã\nThông báo lưu trú\nĐăng ký, quản lý cư trú\nTTHC không được luật giao cho địa phương quy định hoặc quy định chi tiết\nCông dân Việt Nam, Cán bộ, công chức, viên chức, Doanh nghiệp, Tổ chức (không bao gồm doanh nghiệp, HTX), Hợp tác xã\nCông an Xã\nViệc thông báo lưu trú được thực hiện trước 23 giờ của ngày bắt đầu lưu trú; trường hợp người đến lưu trú sau 23 giờ thì việc thông báo lưu trú được thực hiện trước 08 giờ ngày hôm sau; trường hợp ông, bà, cha, mẹ, vợ, chồng, con, cháu, anh, chị, em ruột đến lưu trú nhiều lần thì chỉ cần thông báo lưu trú một lần.\nKhông có thông tin	[0.07776591,0.0909681,-0.0427886,-0.05035691,0.06202241,0.022110725,-0.1116397,0.07022267,0.028480023,0.06838755,0.03427874,-0.007964129,0.0022785994,-0.009433715,-0.005955447,0.03501475,-0.04688889,-0.02825645,-0.00058027386,-0.08355063,-0.026047584,-0.030080272,-0.049384665,0.008221799,0.11228633,0.035195623,0.030491972,-0.015606468,0.028867219,0.010217207,-0.054630008,-0.015514633,0.006052754,0.018826963,0.1044667,0.064451165,0.062416647,-0.032061026,0.011080122,-0.0542097,-0.027066935,-0.063399635,0.058843028,0.028879786,0.019895738,0.05281084,-0.012417394,-0.036889218,-0.09662163,0.0070513855,0.054232955,-0.0058983173,0.046309143,0.07745764,-0.07014473,0.01171019,0.022264276,0.03181428,-0.037524622,0.0020711566,-0.040823802,0.0017359627,-0.0928213,0.013385024,-0.08630991,0.077433474,-0.10431866,-0.08210752,0.0643535,-0.019384705,-0.019167377,-0.018859563,-0.07170872,0.06449562,-0.00081905833,0.031741705,0.01507011,0.116220854,0.07050533,-0.048035033,0.014623659,0.065571934,-0.0014581841,-0.018003449,-0.06797489,-0.04650707,-0.04869568,0.07175851,-0.034380734,0.0029718957,0.085747406,-0.047255322,0.05843744,-0.015353092,-0.004724943,-0.07192527,-0.009565534,0.07702881,-0.017933354,0.016945597,0.0957997,0.09683562,-0.10761699,0.040024668,-0.053643066,0.056918982,0.015683236,-0.06681696,0.025330057,-0.018414034,-0.029544964,0.029024113,-0.031627554,-0.07875